      "status": "verified",
      "text": "Name: Java API Docs Generator\nDescription: Adds SpringDoc OpenAPI documentation to existing Spring Boot services with minimal disruption and auto-detected API coverage.\nOrganization: SEL Engineering\nStatus: verified\nVersion: 1.0.0\nTechnologies: Java, Spring Boot, SpringDoc, OpenAPI\nPrimary specialization: api_documentation\nDomain specific: Swagger UI, OpenAPI 3.0, Zero-Impact Integration\nTasks: Add SpringDoc Dependency - Injects the OpenAPI UI dependency and updates project configuration.; Generate Swagger Configuration - Creates OpenAPI configuration and application properties for interactive docs.\nDocumentation: See attached agent.md Point the skill at a Spring Boot project path and let it add API documentation in place. v1.0.0 initial ultra-minimal release.",
