      "text": "Name: Java Backend Code Generator\nDescription: Generates Spring Boot backend components from embedded entity specifications, including controllers, services, repositories, DTOs, and validation-aware infrastructure.\nOrganization: SEL Engineering\nStatus: verified\nVersion: 1.0.0\nTechnologies: Java, Spring Boot, JPA, Lombok\nPrimary specialization: code_generation\nDomain specific: Backend CRUD, Entity Scaffolding, Infrastructure Automation\nTasks: Generate Backend Components - Creates entities, repositories, services, controllers, DTOs, and exception classes from embedded configuration.; Verify Runnable Setup - Checks dependencies, H2 configuration, and application startup requirements for generated code.\nDocumentation: See attached agent.md Configure entities and generation mode inside the skill, then run it against your backend project. v1.0.0 adds whole-project and selective generation modes.",
